Permanently deletes the specified domain and all of its data

Source: R/opensearchservice_operations.R
opensearchservice_delete_domain.Rd

Permanently deletes the specified domain and all of its data. Once a domain is deleted, it cannot be recovered.

opensearchservice_delete_domain(DomainName)

Arguments

DomainName

[required] The name of the domain you want to permanently delete.

Value

A list with the following syntax:
